      <title>特朗普誓言削减社会保障税以吸引老年人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/trump-vows-to-cut-taxes-on-social-security-in-bid-to-woo-seniors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普承诺取消老年人社会保障税，此举将减少部分美国老年人的税费，但会进一步给尚未退休人士的福利造成压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/trump-vows-to-cut-taxes-on-social-security-in-bid-to-woo-seniors</guid>
